fields.name: ApiKey
fields.description: The API key used to authenticate with Request-Response endpoint.

fields.name: BatchSize
fields.description: Number between 1 and 10000 describing maximum number of rows for every Azure ML RRS execute request. Default is 1000.

fields.name: Endpoint
fields.description: The Request-Response execute endpoint of the Azure Machine Learning web service.

fields.name: InputRequestName
fields.description: Label for the input request object.

fields.name: Inputs
fields.description: The inputs for the Azure Machine Learning web service endpoint.

fields.name: NumberOfParallelRequests
fields.description: The number of parallel requests that will be sent per partition of your job to the machine learning service. Default is 1.

fields.name: OutputResponseName
fields.description: Label for the output request object.

fields.name: Outputs
fields.description: A list of outputs from the Azure Machine Learning web service endpoint execution.
